’Щ@64af86ad36035b95f64147d776226758ce1693e78ff3403e0aa6f10cb404e56fЪTitle: title: str camel-case
Path: Examples
Content:
convert a string to camelCase
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
>  'NuShell' | str camel-case
nuShell

```
convert a string to camelCase
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 'this-is-the-first-case' | str camel-case
thisIsTheFirstCase

```
convert a string to camelCase
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
>  'this_is_the_second_case' | str camel-case
thisIsTheSecondCase

```
convert a column from a table to camelCase
